prasiddhimeva darśayati dhārmiketi hyantena | anugrahakāriṇi hi laukikā dhārmikaśabdaṃ prayuñjānā dṛśyante | pīḍākāriṇi cādhārmikaśabdam | yaśca dharmam ācarati sa dhārmikaḥ | tad yady anugraho dharmaḥ tad evam upapadyate nānyatheti | etad eva bhagavato vyāsasyāpy abhimatam iti darśayati tatheti prayojanamantena | nirviṣayaprayogāsambhavāt tadviṣayam idamā pratinirdiśati | tad ayam arthaḥ viśiṣṭaviṣaye puṇyapāpapadadvaye ācaṇḍālaṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ vidyamāne tenaiva dharmādharmapramitisiddher anarthakaṃ śāstram iti | nanv evaṃ puṇyapāpapramāṇakau dharmādharmāvuktau na lokapramāṇakau | naivam | tatprayogasyaiva lokāyattatvāt | tasmādayam anupālambha iti ||
